    "name": "Flutter-Firebase API Documentation",
    "description": "App Name: GrowTown\n\nAPI Documentation for the GrowTown Flutter + Firebase mobile application.\n\nVersion: 1.0.0  \nBase URL: https://growtown.firebaseapp.com  \nAuthentication: Firebase Phone Authentication (Bearer Token)  \nLast Updated: 2026-01-23\n\nNote: API requests and responses are representative examples. Actual Firebase operations are handled via Flutter Firebase SDK.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
